I hope that the Federal Reserve’s activities in the areas of small   business, commercial real estate, and workforce development that I described have given you an   insight into how we are trying to mitigate the economic downturn’s impact on communities.  We   look forward to continued dialogue and partnership with you as we seek to find ways to hasten   recovery and rebuild communities.
